================================================================================

  • Molecular structures are streamed at runtime from the RCSB Protein Data Bank
    (coordinate data is CC0) and from PubChem. No structure files are stored in
    this repository.

  • The 3D viewer is Mol* (https://molstar.org), MIT-licensed. Its prebuilt
    bundle is copied from the `molstar` npm package at build time into
    public/vendor/ (gitignored) and is not committed here.

  • Simulations embedded from PhET Interactive Simulations are licensed CC BY 4.0:
    "PhET Interactive Simulations, University of Colorado Boulder,
    https://phet.colorado.edu".

  • Videos (YouTube) and podcast (Spotify) are embedded via the providers' own
    iframes and are never rehosted. Rights remain with their owners.
